items.title: Air India to recalibrate plans on Turkish Technic's maintenance works for its wide-body planes
items.description: Heavy maintenance works of some of the airline’s wide-body B777s and B787s are done by Turkiye-based Turkish Technic

items.title: IndiGo places firm order for 30 additional Airbus A350 aircraft
items.description: In March 2025, IndiGo began preparing for its long-haul operations with the introduction of six temporarily leased wide body aircraft, deliveries of which will be concluded by 2026.

items.title: Air India in talks with Airbus, Boeing for new major aircraft deal: Report
items.description: The ongoing order discussions, according to two sources, could encompass several hundred aircraft across different size categories

items.title: Patanjali Ayurved denies receiving MCA notice on proposed investigation over financial deals
items.description: While Patanjali Ayurved is a closely held company, its unit Patanjali Foods Ltd. is publicly traded. Its shares have declined close to 10% so far this month.
